import "core-js/modules/es6.regexp.split";
import "core-js/modules/es6.regexp.split";
/**
 * 系统某些功能隐藏模块
 */

var H = {
  map: {}
};

H.init = function (_ref) {
  var hides = _ref.hides;
  if (!hides) return;

  for (var array = hides.split(','), i = 0, len = array.length; i < len; i++) {
    H.map[array[i]] = true;
  }
};

H.show = function (key) {
  return !(H.map[key] || false);
};

export default window.$_H = H;

};
